  "llm_validation_hints": {
    "_": "Turbine disc with fir-tree slots: sketch_profile revolved body + sketch_profile extruded cutter + composition circular pattern + boolean cut. Disc profile uses ordered R-Z polygon with hub(60-120mm, 76mm thick), tapered web(120-215mm, 44→30mm thick via single sloped segment), rim(215-250mm, 60mm thick). Fir-tree slot: 3 neck/lobe pairs, mouth half-width 4mm, first lobe half-width 7mm, second lobe half-width 6mm, root half-width 4mm, depth 20mm. All interior vertices filleted at 1mm radius. 60 slots at radius 250mm, rotate_copies=true, extrude both directions for full Z-span cut."
  }
